Package com.adobe.fontengine.inlineformatting

Class TypographicCase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.fontengine.inlineformatting.TypographicCase
  • public final class TypographicCase
extends java.lang.Object
    Enumerated values for ElementAttribute.typographicCase. Glyphs have typographic case, which describe their shape and their spacing. This notion is distinct from the notion of character case (which is uppercase, lowercase, or caseless).
